  <summary date="2021-03-11T20:24:47Z" status="Introduced in Senate">End Taxpayer Subsidies for Drug Ads Act

This bill prohibits a tax deduction for expenses relating to direct-to-consumer advertising of prescription drugs.

Direct-to-consumer advertising is any dissemination, by or on behalf of a sponsor of a prescription drug product, of an advertisement that is in regard to the drug product and primarily targeted to the general public.</summary>
